Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以朝陽升起為時限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前達成目的 並逃離瑞迪雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都不許…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了！艾莉莎公主闖進來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去我們會被包圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得…這附近應該有應急用的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然這種地方都埋伏了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:00:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:00:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蕾爾 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一口氣衝過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:00:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:52.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しみに囚われた魂達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:52.51,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}為悲傷所困的靈魂們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:02:02.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:02:02.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}因無盡的憎恨而呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:07.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}迷いの森を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:07.60,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穿過迷惘的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界照らしに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們將去照亮世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:16.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絶望抱きしめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:16.67,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}會去擁抱絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}說明還未放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:27.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}孤独超えたら信じあえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:27.27,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}當我們跨越孤獨便可互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絆離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放開這份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:34.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望という眩しい重さに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:34.96,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望炫目而又沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:40.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中握有不被壓倒的熱誠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:47.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想い  光へ  何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:47.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思念化作光芒 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.16,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至生命耗盡
