Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴爾托羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎公主好像闖入城了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1a&H9f\blur13\fs35\fad(0,2000)\3c&H3D3D41&\pos(120.685,714.667)}淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已在城內大街小巷配置了一千名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把廣場點亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台可準備好了 艾莉莎公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可得讓我盡興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 追不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍捲風的前進速度在加快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是被瑞迪雷克拉過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這樣 連靠近都沒戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去攪和攪和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎公主正為了救你往這裡趕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？我是誰呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要說的話 算是艾莉莎公主的支持者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 她犧牲自己的士兵來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就跟別的傢伙一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為支持者這讓我有點遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那你就不配支持她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要真是艾莉莎的支持者就應該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底是要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不會來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你說艾莉莎公主要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會為了私人的感情而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是身為人民公僕的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直教導艾莉莎 在這個時代更應該嚴格遵守這點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 她從一開始就知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 艾莉莎才是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從外城牆進來應該早就能到廣場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我準備馬車！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能這麼追著龍捲風 往瑞迪雷克的方向去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…我們要怎麼對付龍捲風呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米寶說到重點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有讓龍捲風停下來的方法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是讓它停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要淨化那個龍捲風里承載的污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是說過 每個人都帶有污穢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們一直是規誡著自己心中的污穢生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污穢是自己應該與之戰鬥的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果規誡不住的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們就會自己吸引憑魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污穢的強烈程度是每個人各自不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形式也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都擁有十到二十的污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人累積到百就爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人會積攢到千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷你是想說你能分辨這些污穢的大小程度麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括那個龍捲風？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在裡面的東西是個什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍無法淨化 艾德娜和扎比達還有萊拉都這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我認為那不是因為龍沒辦法淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因為過去還沒有哪個導師能接受龍的污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑現在的史雷 能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不試試看我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我打算試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是 你沒能完全接受的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我會死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 有你們大家在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷已經成長為如此強大 如此出色的導師了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米凱爾大人 您沒能實現的夢想 說不定有朝一日能得以實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾莉莎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父王 不…海蘭德王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我為了向您請願而直接拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蘭德正面臨前所未有的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的怨恨 妒忌 嫉妒 憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些感情造就了現在這個災厄的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們應該終止一切爭鬥 讓人民從不安中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是打破這個僵局的唯一辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你過來 讓我好好看看你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你長得越來越像你母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父王…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…父王…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是沒想到你會直接衝著國王來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確擒賊先擒王是戰略的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們是父女 導致我漏掉了這一選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的修行還遠遠不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是來弒父的 是來進行協商的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜帶兵襲擊這裡 有誰會相信你這番話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 巴爾托羅卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛國通敵 暗殺國王未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就由我親自…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制裁你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾莉莎…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父王…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父王！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 拿起你的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們騎士團不是很了不起麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼 我都不會殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這殺害王的罪人 就獨自在牢房裡終老吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,損害國家利益 只會高唱理想的幻想家公主和我相比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得民眾會支持誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算散佈謠言 煽動民眾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望妳稱這為戰略
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是你的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴爾托羅閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您為什麼這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是因為信任國家 才不惜與戰友兵戎相見的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別被騙了！這是…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了 巴爾托羅卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎公主 你說你不會殺了我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾莉莎殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！往王宮跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼玩意兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞迪雷克這下要完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎 能聽見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你作為從士來支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能來我這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米庫里歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路茲洛希維·瑞雷伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.86,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Danger hides in shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.86,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}危險潛藏在陰影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的能淨化龍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:45.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}this wilderness of lost and found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:45.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}潛藏在這片失與得的荒原中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:49.08,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}But in this closing darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:49.08,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}但在逼近的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的史雷一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:54.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}among this terror there's a light we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:54.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}在這恐懼之中  我們能看到一線光明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是還沒人淨化成功過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.21,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.21,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就由我們來打破！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}We still have a chance to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們仍有機會做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貫穿一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:09.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}I feel us all rising up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:09.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我能感受到我們正在崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼穹的十二連！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.13,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Now, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.13,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}此刻  不要放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:20.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even though the odds have left us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:20.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}即便我們失去勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:28.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Feeling so small, but we can't stop now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:28.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望如此渺小  但我們不能停下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅澤 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:32.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}I know there's a light,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:32.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我知道這束光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.69,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}don't let it fade out, it's our heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.69,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}別讓它熄滅  這是我們的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿污穢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要淨化你的靈魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.49,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}We are not defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.49,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們尚未被戰勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:50.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}we're not losing, in these flames of war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:50.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}在這片戰火之中  我們尚未失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:55.98,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}We're rising up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:55.98,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們正在崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:17:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅澤！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…還…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是你 羅澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是風之骨的頭領…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太慢了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷 也把污穢傳送給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我給你連上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:51.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}I know there's a light,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:51.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我知道這束光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:57.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}the only shining in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:57.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}是我們心中唯一的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撐住啊 大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:04.34,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Standing here, in this place where freedom lives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:04.34,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們站在這裡  站在這片自由的土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:08.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}I know there's a light,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:08.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我知道這束光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:14.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}don't let it fade out, it's our heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:14.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}別讓它熄滅  這是我們的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}We are not defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們尚未被戰勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:25.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}we're not losing, in these flames of war
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:25.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們尚未失敗  在這片戰火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:31.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}We're rising up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:31.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們正在崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…她們只是失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然接近極限…她們兩個人都撐下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把龍淨化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能淨化你哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都這副慘樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為這樣就能拯救世界那可大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有人能阻止吾主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾主要讓世間一切被污穢籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界即將迎來末日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}もうどうしようもないって事もある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.48,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}總會有著無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}なるようにしかならなかったり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}卻又只能順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:36.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}また押し寄せてくる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:36.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}這個緊逼過來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:42.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ただどうやって受け止めたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:42.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}要讓人該如何接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}It's mean to be
